    stringr (>= 1.0.0), 
    sspse (>= 0.6.0),
    estimatr (>= 0.20.0), 
    chords (>= 0.90.0),
    RDS,
    NSUM,
    fastDummies, 
    MultiRNG, 
    testthat, 
    methods
Suggests: 
    covr (>= 3.5.0),
    DeclareDesign (>= 0.20.0)
